 Syntax:  .ustat  or  .ustat <user>

Results:  Allows you to get stats on a specified user. Name, desc, gender,
          email, commands total, logins total, time online, flags set,
          profile, etc.. If no user is specified, it will show your stats.
          <user> is case INsensitive, (meaning it doesn't matter if you
          type it upper or lower case)

See also: set, examine, set_profile
